## ğŸ› ï¸ Configuration

Edit `_config.yml` to tune your site:

```yaml
title: "My Awesome Site"
description: "A blazing fast Jekyll site powered by Karbon Twilight."
theme: jekyll-twilight
author:
  name: "Your Name"
  email: you@example.com
# Social links
social:
  twitter: your_handle
  github:  your_username
# Color customization
sass:
  style: compressed
  load_paths:
    - _sass
```

Override CSS variables in `assets/css/JekyllTwilight.css`:

```css
:root {
  --primary-color: #e67e22;
  --accent-color:  #3498db;
}
```

